{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"metadata":{"title":"Layouts","roleHeading":"Article","role":"article","modules":[{"name":"OUDSComponents"}]},"kind":"article","abstract":[{"text":"Some components can be used for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"layouts","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"level":3,"anchor":"Colored-Surface","text":"Colored Surface","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Colored backgrounds use surface colors to maximize the contrast with content."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The colors of several OUDS components (for instance "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSLink","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":") are automatically adjusted if they are placed on "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSColoredSurface","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"To do so, some tokens associated with these specific colors can be customized and are identified with the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Mono","type":"text"}]},{"text":" suffix (for instance ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"buttonColorBgDefaultEnabledMono"}]},{"text":" of ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider"}]},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":4,"anchor":"How-it-works","text":"How it works","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"According to the color, the ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSColoredSurface","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" component adds in SwiftUI environment two flags:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"oudsUseMonochrome"},{"type":"text","text":": to inform a component that needs to use mono version of tokens"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"oudsOnColoredSurface"},{"text":": to inform a component it is placed on colored surface even if the mono is off","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":4,"anchor":"How-to-use","text":"How to use","type":"heading"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ The folowing view has a colored background \"modeOnStatusPositiveEmphasized\" with","    \/\/ - a text with the color adapted according to the adjusted colorScheme      ","    \/\/ - a button that uses the mono version of tokens","","    \/\/ As view","    OUDSColoredSurface(color: theme.colorModes.modeOnStatusPositiveEmphasized) {","        VStack {","            Text(\"Status Positive Emphasized\")","            .oudsForegroundColor(theme.colors.colorContentDefault)","","            OUDSButton(text: \"Button\") {}","        }","    }","","    \/\/ As view modifier","","    VStack {","        Text(\"Status Positive Emphasized\")","        .oudsForegroundColor(theme.colors.colorContentDefault)","","        OUDSButton(text: \"Button\") {}","    }","    .oudsColoredSurface(theme.colorModes.modeOnStatusPositiveEmphasized)"]},{"level":3,"anchor":"Divider","text":"Divider","type":"heading"},{"level":4,"anchor":"How-it-works","text":"How it works","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A divider is used to separate content elements in a view. Two kinds of divider are proposed:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSHorizontalDivider"},{"type":"text","text":" To separate elements stacked vertivally (VStask)."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSVerticalDivider"},{"text":" To separate elements stacked Horizontally (HStask).","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A divider can be colored using color enumerated in the "},{"code":"OUDSDividerColor","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":4,"anchor":"How-to-use","text":"How to use","type":"heading"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ Add a vertical divider between items","HStack {","    Text(\"Hello wolrd!\")","    OUDSVerticalDivider(color: .brandPrimary)","    Text(\"Happy to see you\")","}","","\/\/ Add an horizontal divider between items","VStack {","    Text(\"Hello wolrd!\")","    OUDSHorizontalDivider(color: .brandPrimary)","    Text(\"Happy to see you\")","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/layouts"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Layouts"},"references":{"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The catalog of all components provided by OUDS. It contains also "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View"},{"type":"text","text":" extensions and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewModifiers"},{"type":"text","text":" to apply tokens and styles on components and higher-level views."}],"title":"OUDSComponents","type":"topic","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSButton":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton"},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layout with text only, icon only or text with icon."}],"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSButton"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSButton"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsbutton","title":"OUDSButton"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSLink":{"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSLink","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" proposes layout with text only or text with icon.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It also proposes layout to navigate forward or backward. The link can be displayed in ","type":"text"},{"code":"small","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"code":"default","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" size.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSLink","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSLink"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSLink"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"OUDSLink","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudslink","kind":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSColoredSurface":{"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSColoredSurface","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Used to define if a content is used on a colored surface."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSColoredSurface","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscoloredsurface","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","title":"OUDSColoredSurface","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSColoredSurface","type":"topic"}}}